sequenceDiagram
    participant KFTO as KFTO PyTorchJob<br/>Controller
    participant Pod as Training Pod
    participant AccelLaunch as accelerate_launch.py<br/>Container Entrypoint
    participant SFTTrainer as sft_trainer.py<br/>Core Training Engine
    participant PVC_M as PVC<br/>Model Weights
    participant PVC_D as PVC<br/>Training Data
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PVC_O as PVC<br/>Output/Checkpoints
    participant Tracker as Experiment Tracker<br/>(Aim/MLflow/ClearML)

    Note over KFTO,Pod: Flow 1: Training Job Execution

    KFTO->>Pod: Create PyTorchJob Pod<br/>Kubernetes API, TLS 1.3<br/>ServiceAccount Auth
    Pod->>AccelLaunch: Start container CMD<br/>Read /etc/config/config.json

    AccelLaunch->>AccelLaunch: Parse JSON config<br/>Detect GPU count<br/>Configure FSDP defaults

    AccelLaunch->>SFTTrainer: subprocess: accelerate launch<br/>sft_trainer.py with args

    SFTTrainer->>PVC_M: Load model weights<br/>Local filesystem mount
    PVC_M-->>SFTTrainer: Model artifacts

    SFTTrainer->>PVC_D: Load training data<br/>Local filesystem mount
    PVC_D-->>SFTTrainer: Training dataset

    opt Model not on PVC (fallback)
        SFTTrainer->>HFHub: GET model/tokenizer<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN
        HFHub-->>SFTTrainer: Model artifacts
    end

    SFTTrainer->>SFTTrainer: Data preprocessing<br/>(handlers, templates,<br/>tokenization)

    loop Training Loop (epochs x steps)
        SFTTrainer->>GPU: Forward/backward pass<br/>PCIe/NVLink
        GPU-->>SFTTrainer: Gradients

        SFTTrainer->>SFTTrainer: Trainer Controller<br/>Evaluate rules<br/>(early stopping, thresholds)

        opt Checkpoint interval
            SFTTrainer->>PVC_O: Save checkpoint<br/>Local filesystem
        end

        opt Tracker enabled
            SFTTrainer->>Tracker: Push metrics<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        end
    end

    SFTTrainer->>PVC_O: Save final model<br/>+ LoRA adapters
    SFTTrainer-->>AccelLaunch: Training complete

    opt vLLM post-processing
        AccelLaunch->>AccelLaunch: Post-process LoRA adapters<br/>for vLLM compatibility
    end

    AccelLaunch->>Pod: Write termination log<br/>/dev/termination-log
    Pod-->>KFTO: Pod completed<br/>Exit code 0 (success)<br/>or 1 (user error)<br/>or 203 (internal error)

    Note over Pod,GPU: Flow 2: Multi-GPU FSDP Training

    AccelLaunch->>AccelLaunch: Detect num_gpus > 1<br/>Apply FSDP defaults

    AccelLaunch->>SFTTrainer: Launch with accelerate<br/>--num_processes=N

    SFTTrainer->>SFTTrainer: Initialize FSDP<br/>process group

    par NCCL Rendezvous
        SFTTrainer->>SFTTrainer: Rank 0 master<br/>port 29500/TCP
        Note right of SFTTrainer: plaintext TCP<br/>NCCL/Gloo backend
    end

    loop FSDP Training
        par All Ranks
            SFTTrainer->>GPU: Sharded forward/backward<br/>PCIe/NVLink per rank
            GPU-->>SFTTrainer: Local gradients
        end
        SFTTrainer->>SFTTrainer: All-reduce gradients<br/>NCCL 29500/TCP plaintext
    end
